{
  "stem": "27129.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was ashame-- no, I was a stupid teenager.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I wanted to look good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So it was really cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One morning, I went to work, you know, I froze my cheek and-- and-- this ear.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I still have trouble with that ear.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was really cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was no joke.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Just to walk from the-- from the quarters where I lived, you know, to the factory, it was like from here to the next street.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, it's-- it was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But, as I say, when you're young, you know, things are different than when you get older.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He became a, uh, a car mechanic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were together there, and then we went from there, from Guzar, where the Polish Army was organize-- organizing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we couldn't get into the army, so in order to leave, so we had to go and look for other things, you know, where we can settle down for the time being steady, because we never thought we would be able to get out from Russia.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we went to [NON-ENGLISH], a city [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And over there, my brother went to work as a mechanic in the-- in the truck, uh-- how do you call it?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Oh, there were about 60 trucks, you know, a fleet from 60 trucks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, they were holding stuff.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went to work in a sugar factory as electrician.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, uh, over there, we-- we worked, and it was-- it was not easy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like in the weekends, you know, in the winter time, they come-- you had to go unload trucks, you know, with merchandise that come, you know, heavy stuff.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you work for nothing, because it's for the government.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
